{
  "stem": "2581.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were taken up to another-- across the street-- but it was a pile of stones and on that pile of stones, a man stood that introduce himself as [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now [NON-ENGLISH] was Himmler's son-in-law, and it seems that they were concerned if we would resist because they tried to-- I wouldn't say appease us-- but keep us calm.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He told us in German that we're going to work, being shipped to work, where we will have [GERMAN], apples and oranges and anything that we desire, as long as we will devote ourselves for the good of the Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "At the same time, they asked if anyone has any diamonds or jewelry, you better give it to them now because we will be searched.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "People, whatever they had hidden-- I don't know if everybody, but things were being given to them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that was continued for the groups and these were the groups that were being-- these 300 people are being sent to-- I think it was 300.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's what it is in my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But from these supposedly healthy, work-capable people, they had picked 20 people that were sent to Chelmno to dig graves for those that remained in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Those 20 people never came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Some people, I remember distinctly, there was [NON-ENGLISH], my friend that lives here in Florida with a brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was two brothers, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I don't remember-- I just remember-- but they dug the grave, they also dug a grave for themselves, where they were later shot and thrown into that grave.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were women, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I became a housekeeper where I took care.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
